{"tid":697364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[利字當頭] 左派組織資源足 開足水喉培植小花","createTime":"2018-06-11T02:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T02:29:34.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97ebddfa3971fb6c8f9afda27fdd30ee41c1ec31","tid":697364,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"曾為鍾樹根助理的植潔鈴勝出補選，可謂與天時、地利與人和有關。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選民於區議會選舉一向重民生多於政治</strong></span>，事實上現時社會除一地兩檢外，未見其他重大爭議會激發選民投票意欲，在此情況下，有左派「鐵票」護身的植潔鈴選情早已佔優。<br />\n<br />\n而建制派與民主派的最大分別，至少在選舉資源高下立見。植潔鈴在2015年區選敗陣後，繼續留守佳曉作戰，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民建聯除了有資源「養活」她在原區復仇，亦向當區選民大開水喉，有民主派指地區活動的禮品多不勝數，在選民多為公屋居民的基層區，明顯有「甜頭」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>30歲的植潔鈴的外型標緻亦是賣點</strong></span>。鄭泳舜於九西補選勝出的啟示之一，正是賣相同樣也重要，植潔鈴這次選戰亦大打健康乖乖女形象，相對其餘兩名女對手，無疑較為搶眼，而且網戰亦厲害，不排除亦吸納部份游離選民支持。"},{"pid":"c7113ad562d9e4bba87387245da41f1c762989ef","tid":697364,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58302800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58302800&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a9919efe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58302800&h=f30449fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58302800</a>"},{"pid":"00b37a7b07dcf81e61a6feb441922fc14583dfe2","tid":697364,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"班選民真係重民生定係重蛇齋餅粽呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09b64a037c19d6ffef1f26aacf18a8d22703304","tid":697364,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}